text: Lars Olof Jonathan Söderblom (), born 15 January 1866 in Trönö, Sweden, dead 12 July 1931 in Uppsala, Sweden was a Swedish Lutheran clergyman. He was the Church of Sweden Archbishop of Uppsala between 1914-1931 In 1930, he was awarded the 1930 Nobel Peace Prize. ==References== Category:1866 births Category:1931 deaths Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
